538
00:32:52,563 --> 00:32:53,857
- I'm not telling you.
- Why not?

539
00:32:53,961 --> 00:32:56,057
Because he told me not to help you.

540
00:32:56,163 --> 00:32:59,059
How the hell did Gabriel find you,
