566
00:34:06,402 --> 00:34:11,596
You told her she'd never
spend another lonely minute.

567
00:34:14,003 --> 00:34:17,098
I miss you so much.

568
00:34:17,405 --> 00:34:20,302
You made me try so hard.

569
00:34:20,409 --> 00:34:24,603
All I wanted was to be the man
you thought I was.

570
00:34:24,711 --> 00:34:27,006
Now it's too late.

571
00:34:27,111 --> 00:34:29,307
Nothing matters anymore.

572
00:34:29,414 --> 00:34:32,507
It's not too late.

573
00:34:32,613 --> 00:34:34,510
Tell him...

574
00:34:34,616 --> 00:34:36,809
this is all meant to happen.

575
00:34:36,918 --> 00:34:38,911
Everything happened for a reason.

576
00:34:39,020 --> 00:34:40,814
She said it's never too late,

577
00:34:40,917 --> 00:34:43,713
and that everything has happened
for a reason.

578
00:34:43,820 --> 00:34:45,614
She wants you to help me, Ethan.

579
00:34:45,722 --> 00:34:47,316
Ok, that's what means
something right now.

580
00:34:47,421 --> 00:34:51,015
Now please tell me where
Gabriel took those kids.

581
00:34:51,125 --> 00:34:52,320
The dedication.

582
00:34:52,425 --> 00:34:54,820
He wanted them to be
part of the lantern walk.

583
00:34:54,926 --> 00:34:58,222
He said it would be good for them
if they were part of something.

584
00:34:58,329 --> 00:35:02,622
I mean, you didn't tell me
she was here!

585
00:35:02,728 --> 00:35:05,325
I'm sorry!

586
00:35:08,132 --> 00:35:10,728
I'm sorry.

587
00:35:18,038 --> 00:35:20,735
I love you.

588
00:35:37,646 --> 00:35:41,042
Ladies and gentlemen,
if I can have your attention, please...

589
00:35:41,149 --> 00:35:45,045
you all know me, I'm mayor Milio,
