591
00:35:50,355 --> 00:35:51,452
Mel, hey.

592
00:35:51,555 --> 00:35:52,851
Jim, it's me.

593
00:35:52,955 --> 00:35:55,453
I need you to find Kristen
and the other kids.

594
00:35:55,559 --> 00:35:58,654
Mel, there's no signal up here.
I can't here you.

595
00:35:58,760 --> 00:35:59,853
No, hello?

596
00:35:59,961 --> 00:36:01,254
Mel?

597
00:36:01,362 --> 00:36:03,855
Oh, Jim?!

598
00:36:06,664 --> 00:36:09,960
Can you go any faster?

599
00:36:11,465 --> 00:36:14,560
We are people from different
parts of the county,

600
00:36:14,669 --> 00:36:16,561
different parts of the state,

601
00:36:16,669 --> 00:36:18,364
and we're all here this evening

602
00:36:18,471 --> 00:36:22,066
